        <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed mb-6">The differential speed between the decanter bowl and scroll is the key to the function of a decanter centrifuge. The differential speed has important functional benefits to the equipment user. In advanced decanter control, the differential speed is key to fine-tuning the decanter operation and safety features.</p>
        <p class="text-text-light text-sm italic">by Sanjay Prabhu MSME, Engineering Manager, Dolphin Centrifuge</p>
